description: Retrieves a credential report for the Amazon Web Services account. For more information about the credential report, see Getting credential reports in the IAM User Guide.

nested_items.name: Content
nested_items.description: Contains the credential report. The report is Base64-encoded.

nested_items.name: ReportFormat
nested_items.description: The format (MIME type) of the credential report.

nested_items.name: GeneratedTime
nested_items.description: The date and time when the credential report was created, in ISO 8601 date-time format.
